              <div class="problems">
                  <div id="problem-type-or-description">
                      <p class="problem">A car travels <code><var>distance</var></code> meters in <code><var>time</var></code> seconds.</p>
                      <p class="question">What is the average speed of the car?</p>
                      <p class="solution">distance / time</p>
                  </div>
              </div>

              <div class="hints">
                  <p>Remember, the average speed is distance over time.</p>
                  <p>We are given that distance=<code><var>distance</code></var> meters and time=<code><var>time</code></var> seconds.</p>
                  <p>Substitue and calculate the velocity, which is <code><var>distance / time </code></var> m/s.</p>
              </div>
